---
const SITE_NAME = "The-Circle";
const DISCORD_INVITE = "https://discord.gg/9rPcHQZ7SH";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Fantasy • {SITE_NAME}</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="The-Circle Fantasy: a league-focused hub for rules, season info, trash talk, and tools."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <header class="top">
        <div class="container nav">
          <a class="brand" href="/">
            <span class="mark"></span>
            <span>{SITE_NAME}</span>
          </a>

          <nav class="links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/discord">Discord</a>
            <a href="/fantasy">Fantasy</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a class="pill" href="/join">Join</a>
          </nav>

          <a class="pill mobileJoin" href="/join">Join</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="container">
        <section class="card">
          <h1>The-Circle League</h1>

          <p class="lead">
            The goal is a clean home base for leagues: rules, season info, standings, and a place for trash talk that isn’t a cluttered mess.
          </p>

          <div class="grid">
            <div class="tile">
              <h2>League hub</h2>
              <p>One place for rules, schedules, payouts, and season notes.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="tile">
              <h2>Trash talk board</h2>
              <p>Keep it fun, keep it readable, and keep it in one spot.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="tile">
              <h2>Tools (coming)</h2>
              <p>Draft helpers, keeper notes, rivalries, weekly summaries.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="tile">
              <h2>Not Yahoo 2.0</h2>
              <p>We’re not trying to rebuild the whole platform. We’re building a better home for your league.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cta">
            <a class="btn primary" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/blog">Read updates</a>
          </div>

          <p class="fine">
            When you’re ready, we can add a real league portal behind login (league pages, members, tools, etc.).
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>

    <style is:global>
      html, body {
        height: 100%;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);

        background-image:
          radial-gradient(900px 500px at 15% 10%, rgba(9,255,3,0.14), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(800px 450px at 85% 15%, rgba(120,170,255,0.18), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(700px 450px at 55% 95%, rgba(255,170,120,0.10), transparent 55%),
          linear-gradient(#070a0f, #070a0f);

        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: 100% 100%;
        background-attachment: fixed;
      }

      .page {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      main {
        flex: 1;
      }

      a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

      .container {
        max-width: 1020px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 18px;
      }

      .top {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        background: rgba(7,10,15,0.55);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      }

      .nav {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .brand {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: center;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .mark {
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #09ff03;
        box-shadow:
          0 0 0 6px rgba(9,255,3,0.12),
          0 0 28px rgba(9,255,3,0.25);
      }

      .links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .links a {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .links a:hover {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      }

      .pill {
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(9,255,3,0.24);
        background: rgba(9,255,3,0.10);
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      }

      .mobileJoin {
        display: none;
      }

      .card {
        margin: 28px 0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 34px;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 6px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .lead {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 78ch;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .tile {
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      .tile p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
        transition: transform 0.12s ease, background 0.12s ease;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      }

      .btn.primary {
        border-color: rgba(9,255,3,0.22);
        background: rgba(9,255,3,0.10);
      }

      .btn.ghost {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      .fine {
        margin-top: 14px;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 820px) {
        .links { display: none; }
        .mobileJoin { display: inline-flex; }
        .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
